{"tid":1275920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣布 新一輪輿論戰即將開始","createTime":"2019-07-02T00:21:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T07:33:11.000Z","uid":73959,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27330c4884ab1930f1f4e4570a89c4edaa828f53","tid":1275920,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"經過琴晚發惡夢 相信各位都好攰<br />\n體力耗得七七八八<br />\n但係！我地唔可以鬆懈住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係文宣組<br />\n今日一岀街已經聽到好多人話後生仔暴力搞亂香港點點點<br />\n我唔叻整圖 但可以提供少少意見<br />\n愚見今日主流聲音主要針對一樣嘢：<br />\n- 就算表達意見都唔應該入立法會搞破壞<br />\n<br />\n針對呢樣文宣工作可以分為三大類：<br />\n<br />\n1. 理性牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 官逼民反 要各位認清元兇係邊個 係政府！二百萬民意全漠視 死三個人當無事發生 仲可以照樣開香檳慶祝！<br />\n- 承認係有破壞但唔係對人 相反警察多次暴力清場 更應該被清算！<br />\n- 所謂衝擊立法會係暴力都不及政暴(政府漠視民意, 呢度可引用返之前已通過的projects, 香港人好善忙, 一定要keep住remind!)<br />\n<br />\n2. 感性牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 如果有人屌班學生 屌返佢哋轉頭 問下佢地做過咩 羞唔羞家！<br />\n- 立場直播連記者都喊<br />\n- 就算入咗立法會 示威者都擺低錢先拎汽水飲<br />\n<br />\n3. 轉移線線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 繼續追擊警方使用不必要武力 工作時冇配戴委任證 不禮貌對待小巴乘客 (唔知發生咩事睇返蘋果live)<br />\n- 撐警遊行示威者同樣暴力 但警察選擇性執法<br />\n- 海濱公園無聲無息被送中<br />\n- 嚟梗嘅國歌法、送中二讀仲有人工島<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多 歡迎再補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位加油！以上唔單止係文宣組工作<br />\n更係我地每一個人要靠word of mouth屌醒身邊仲瞓緊或者被催眠嘅人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712f22272ee23a0f7401a3b541594c0596afdba2","tid":1275920,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:22:08.000Z","msg":"仲有登記做選民！"},{"pid":"40f3a9e8e870b4345411b09c1fa7d0640d7396c5","tid":1275920,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"9fd6b0d6a125d6205e5b4363dbab95d22e4ff146","tid":1275920,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:23:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"752939bb9d133982d951e27e262fca4f1f053fbb","tid":1275920,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:25:29.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca3f880e960dd043011cd0a3f582559ed60a999","tid":1275920,"uid":267594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:34:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c1f899ad518429411479ae97a9b78fd938603d","tid":1275920,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:34:10.000Z","msg":"好撚攰"},{"pid":"67ba9694b2de08da63f761aaccab4fbc7e6ca53b","tid":1275920,"uid":130121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"各位努力<br />\n係各大平台同班五毛網軍死過<br />\n即使有幾多人支持底者反對衝擊立法會都好<br />\n都唔可以比班五毛拉風向"},{"pid":"6275ff9f9ea8d14c807051b96599a4a847d0bb84","tid":1275920,"uid":130121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>各位努力<br />\n係各大平台同班五毛網軍死過<br />\n即使有幾多人支持或者反對衝擊立法會都好<br />\n都唔可以比班五毛拉風向</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c6d0eae29b20f156c188eb8465840f2730f166bf","tid":1275920,"uid":19476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T00:39:28.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;警察內部對林鄭不滿 所以棄守立法會&rdquo;"},{"pid":"c60dbbb787019465c773c608c8e1ed8e4f9bd110","tid":1275920,"uid":97871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T01:46:56.000Z","msg":"Ok Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35730e78234134169b8fda75c948ad1908752e3e","tid":1275920,"uid":73959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T07:32:52.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"